<ul class="list-unstyled list-banners"><li>
        <a class="banner banner-update" title="View the 2021/02/04 8:46am PST Update" href="https://www.androidpolice.com/2021/02/04/chrome-84-brings-new-dino-themed-qr-codes-to-android-and-desktops/#1">
