<p><a href="https://www.androidpolice.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/03/cbx2_hero.jpg" class=" no-style"><img loading="lazy" class="size-hero-size wp-image-756917" src="https://www.androidpolice.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/03/cbx2_hero-728x410.jpg" alt="" width="728" height="410" srcset="https://www.androidpolice.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/03/cbx2_hero-728x410.jpg 728w, https://www.androidpolice.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/03/cbx2_hero-329x185.jpg 329w, https://www.androidpolice.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/03/cbx2_hero-668x376.jpg 668w, https://www.androidpolice.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/03/cbx2_hero-161x91.jpg 161w, https://www.androidpolice.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/03/cbx2_hero-217x122.jpg 217w, https://www.androidpolice.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/03/cbx2_hero.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 728px) 100vw, 728px"/></a></p>
